96
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,439
We will discuss this another day.

97
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,399
Well...

98
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,878
You should rest.

99
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:37,639
Rest well.

100
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,639
(Remember.)

101
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,360
(It's my dream)

102
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,560
